{
  "texts": [
    "Precision, Recall and F1 score was also highest in the co-pilot mode.",
    "In terms of DRP categories, co-pilot mode accuracy improved across most categories including adverse drug reaction, drug-drug interaction, duplication of therapy, inappropriate choice of therapy and omission of drug therapy.",
    "However, performance for co-pilot mode declined in the categories of inappropriate dosage regimen and no indication when pharmacists were unblinded to RAG-LLM response.",
    "Performance of RAG-LLM using Gemini Pro 1.0 and Med-PaLM 2",
    "We also performed a post-hoc experiment using Gemini-Pro 1.0 and Med-PaLM 2."
  ]
}